{
  "stem": "3341.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, Bratislava was the capital town, and there were-- in Bratislava, there were in normal times-- when I say 'normal' times, in the older times-- there were 30,000 or 35,000 Jewish people from 140,000.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all-- lot of his friends there in the capital town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Matter of fact, one of his youngest brother, who was a very good dentist, had his dentistry in Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So went quite often to see him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe he was a little bit over-ambitious and jealous, and he-- his brother lives in the big town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he started to speculate, saying, how can we all come and live in Bratislava?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Such opportunity came along when one of his business friends, a agent of business, suggested to him because he knew that we were financially well off.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he persuaded my father to come to Bratislava to establish a completely different business and be part of the big, good life in the capital town.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because I-- I just finished the fifth class of primary school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The primary school was five years, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I entered the-- the school in 1925.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I finished the first five years of the primary school, then-- then my father arranged.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She resisted, actually, over a year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in the end, she has to give in because my father sold the-- the house, sold the business, which was a gold mine in the little village, and moved to Bratislava and started completely different business-- a fashion business, wholesale, not retail.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I moved to Bratislava, I could have been 10 [INAUDIBLE] 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
